<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
<style>
body{
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    background-color: beige;  
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;

}

.profile-card{
    border: 1px solid white;
    width: 300px;
    text-align: center;
    background:linear-gradient(to right, lavender , #ffafbd );
    padding:30px;
    color: blue;
    border-radius: 25px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 22px black;
             /* y axis x axis spread */
    margin: 30px;         
}


div img {
    border-radius: 50%;
}



</style>

</head>
<body>
    <div class="profile-card">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," height="100" width="100">
        <h1>Abdull</h1>
        <p>Full Stack Developer</p>
    </div>


     <div class="profile-card">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," height="100" width="100">
        <h1>Hasini</h1>
        <p>Frontend Developer</p>
    </div>

     <div class="profile-card">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," height="100" width="100">
        <h1 style="color: red;">Emmanuel</h1>
        <p>Frontend Developer</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
